---
import Ironside from "../layouts/Ironside.astro";
import Placeholder from "../components/PlaceholderImage.astro";
---

<Ironside title="About Ironside Coatings" description="Oakville-owned polyaspartic garage floor specialists. Meet founder Salam Alassali, see our certifications, insurance, and service area." heroType="light">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero-light" style="padding-top:100px">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="kicker">About Ironside</div>
    <h1 class="h-hero mt-3" style="max-width:22ch">Premium garage floors. Oakville-owned, Oakville-operated.</h1>
    <p class="lede mt-4">Salam Alassali started Ironside in 2024 after one too many kitchen-table quotes from contractors who couldn&rsquo;t name the resin system they were installing.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ORIGIN STORY -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split-64" style="align-items:start">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker">Origin story</div>
        <h2 class="h2 mt-2" style="max-width:22ch">Started because the industry needed a standard.</h2>
        <div style="display:grid;gap:20px;margin-top:32px;color:var(--fg1);font-size:18px;line-height:1.6">
          <p>The GTA garage floor market is split two ways. Budget installers slap epoxy over acid-etched concrete and hope it lasts three years. Franchises charge premium prices for systems their crews were certified on six weeks ago.</p>
          <p>Ironside is the middle missing option: a small, tight, Oakville-local shop that only installs what we&rsquo;d pour in our own garage. Polyaspartic. Diamond-ground. Moisture-tested. Warranted for life.</p>
          <p>We are deliberately small. We turn down jobs under $2,500. We turn down property-management portfolios. We turn down out-of-radius drives. That&rsquo;s how every floor gets the same attention.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Placeholder label="Salam Alassali &middot; Owner &middot; Oakville shop" aspect="4/5" variant="warm" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OWNER PROFILE -->
<section class="section section-sm" style="background:var(--color-iron-50);border-top:1px solid var(--color-iron-100);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-iron-100)">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="kicker">Owner</div>
    <h2 class="h2 mt-2 mb-8" style="max-width:20ch">Salam Alassali.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;gap:48px;align-items:center">
      <Placeholder label="Portrait &middot; Salam &middot; 04/26" aspect="1" variant="copper" />
      <div>
        <p class="lede" style="max-width:60ch">&ldquo;My rule is simple: I won&rsquo;t sell a floor I wouldn&rsquo;t install at my own house. That means polyaspartic over diamond-ground concrete, moisture-tested first, backed in writing for life. Anything less is someone else&rsquo;s business.&rdquo;</p>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:40px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid var(--border-default)">
          <div>
            <div class="mono" style="font-size:32px;color:var(--fg1)">14</div>
            <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--fg3);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px">YEARS IN TRADES</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="mono" style="font-size:32px;color:var(--fg1)">320+</div>
            <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--fg3);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px">FLOORS INSTALLED</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="mono" style="font-size:32px;color:var(--fg1)">Oakville</div>
            <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--fg3);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px">BORN &amp; BASED</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CERTIFICATIONS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="kicker">Certifications &amp; insurance</div>
    <h2 class="h2 mt-2 mb-8" style="max-width:20ch">The paperwork that protects you.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px">
      <div class="card" style="padding:32px">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border:1px solid var(--border-default);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-mono-brand);font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">P</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:20px;font-size:18px">Penntek certified</div>
        <div class="p" style="color:var(--fg2);margin-top:8px">Manufacturer-certified applicator &mdash; requirement for lifetime warranty.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:32px">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border:1px solid var(--border-default);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-mono-brand);font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">W</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:20px;font-size:18px">WHMIS 2015</div>
        <div class="p" style="color:var(--fg2);margin-top:8px">Every crew member certified in hazardous materials handling.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:32px">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border:1px solid var(--border-default);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-mono-brand);font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">WSIB</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:20px;font-size:18px">WSIB coverage</div>
        <div class="p" style="color:var(--fg2);margin-top:8px">Workplace Safety &amp; Insurance Board &mdash; full crew coverage on-site.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:32px">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border:1px solid var(--border-default);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-mono-brand);font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)">$5M</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:20px;font-size:18px">Liability insurance</div>
        <div class="p" style="color:var(--fg2);margin-top:8px">$5M general liability policy. Certificate available on request.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INSURANCE COVERAGE -->
<section class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split-64" style="align-items:start">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker">Insurance coverage</div>
        <h2 class="h2 mt-2" style="color:var(--fg-inverse);max-width:20ch">What our policy actually covers.</h2>
        <p class="lede" style="color:var(--color-iron-300);margin-top:16px">Most contractors will show you a certificate. Few explain what it covers. Here&rsquo;s ours in plain English.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dl style="display:grid;gap:16px;margin:0">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;padding:20px;background:var(--color-iron-900);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800)">
            <div class="mono" style="color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;width:80px;flex-shrink:0">$5M</div>
            <div>
              <dt style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-weight:600">General liability</dt>
              <dd class="mono" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-iron-300);margin:4px 0 0">Per-occurrence limit for property damage on your site</dd>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;padding:20px;background:var(--color-iron-900);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800)">
            <div class="mono" style="color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;width:80px;flex-shrink:0">WSIB</div>
            <div>
              <dt style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-weight:600">Worker coverage</dt>
              <dd class="mono" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-iron-300);margin:4px 0 0">Injured crew members are covered by WSIB, not your homeowner policy</dd>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;padding:20px;background:var(--color-iron-900);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800)">
            <div class="mono" style="color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;width:80px;flex-shrink:0">$2M</div>
            <div>
              <dt style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-weight:600">Completed operations</dt>
              <dd class="mono" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-iron-300);margin:4px 0 0">Coverage extends past install date for warranty claims</dd>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;padding:20px;background:var(--color-iron-900);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800)">
            <div class="mono" style="color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;width:80px;flex-shrink:0">HST</div>
            <div>
              <dt style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-weight:600">HST registered</dt>
              <dd class="mono" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-iron-300);margin:4px 0 0">Proper invoices with HST number &mdash; no cash-only discounts</dd>
            </div>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="section section-sm" style="background:var(--color-iron-50);border-top:1px solid var(--color-iron-100);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-iron-100)">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split-64" style="align-items:start">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker">Service area</div>
        <h2 class="h2 mt-2" style="max-width:20ch">Where you&rsquo;ll find us.</h2>
        <p class="lede mt-4">Our shop is on Wyecroft Road in Oakville. We service a 40-minute radius &mdash; tight on purpose.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:32px;padding:24px;background:var(--bg-elevated);border:1px solid var(--border-default)">
          <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--fg3)">SHOP ADDRESS</div>
          <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">1450 Wyecroft Rd, Unit 12</div>
          <div class="p" style="color:var(--fg2);margin-top:4px">Oakville, ON L6L 6M1</div>
          <div class="mono" style="font-size:13px;margin-top:16px">M&ndash;F 8a&ndash;6p &middot; Sat 9a&ndash;2p</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="aspect-ratio:4/3;background:var(--color-iron-950);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800);overflow:hidden">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 500 380" style="width:100%;height:100%">
            <defs><pattern id="g3" width="24" height="24" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M24 0L0 0L0 24" fill="none" stroke="#1F2428" stroke-width="0.5"/></pattern></defs>
            <rect width="500" height="380" fill="#0B0D10"/><rect width="500" height="380" fill="url(#g3)"/>
            <circle cx="250" cy="200" r="145" fill="rgba(217,95,31,0.06)" stroke="#D95F1F" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 5" opacity="0.6"/>
            <circle cx="250" cy="200" r="10" fill="#D95F1F"/><circle cx="250" cy="200" r="20" fill="none" stroke="#D95F1F" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4"/>
            <text x="250" y="178" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="11" fill="#F4F3EF" letter-spacing="2">IRONSIDE HQ</text>
            <text x="250" y="360" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="10" fill="#6B7278" letter-spacing="3">40-MINUTE SERVICE RADIUS</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- IRON-CLAD WARRANTY -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container-narrow" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="kicker plain" style="justify-content:center">Iron-Clad Warranty</div>
    <h2 class="h-hero mt-3" style="max-width:20ch;margin:0 auto">Our handshake is in writing.</h2>
    <p class="lede mt-4" style="margin:16px auto 0">The Iron-Clad Warranty is transferable to the next homeowner, backed by manufacturer-certified systems, and covers delamination, discoloration, and hot-tire pickup for the life of your slab.</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary mt-6">Read the full warranty</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BAND -->
<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker">Let&rsquo;s build yours</div>
        <h2 class="h1 mt-2" style="color:var(--fg-inverse);max-width:22ch">Get a quote from Oakville&rsquo;s polyaspartic specialists.</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;align-items:flex-end">
        <a href="/quote" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" style="min-width:260px">Get my free quote</a>
        <a href="tel:9055550174" class="btn btn-lg btn-ghost-dark" style="min-width:260px">905 &middot; 555 &middot; 0174</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Ironside>
